0.0.1.name: wordpress/embed-script-video-from-goviral-network
0.0.1.description: When plugin Goviral installed, the plugin will insert button Goviral in media bar Post/Page When you click on the button, can you see a pop-up. Copy script embed Goviral Video and paste in Textbox. Click Add Video, then shortcode will auto create and insert to content.
